high_descs: Turn left walk across the room and head to the counter beside the stove
Pick up the apple on the counter
Turn to your right then walk forward, then face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave, put in and out the apple then close the microwave
Turn to your right then cross the room head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put inside the apple then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the warm apple on the fridge

high_descs: Turn left, then turn right, and walk across the kitchen until you reach the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up an apple from the counter.
Walk over to the stove and look up at the microwave above it.
Warm the apple in the microwave and then take it out.
Turn around, turn left, then walk to the fridge.
Place the apple on the top shelf of the fridge, to the left of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed apple in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around and move towards the gas
pick up the apple to the left of the gas
turn right and head towards the gas
place  the apple in the microwave to cook and then take it out
turn right and head towards the fridge
place the cooked apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a cooked apple in the fridge
